fix: customers grid 500 error and add clear-dashboard reset endpoint

- Fixed get_customers() - search param defaulted to FastAPI Query object
  instead of None when not passed, causing AttributeError on .strip()
- Added POST /api/settings/clear-dashboard admin endpoint that safely
  deletes all subscriptions, credits, cancellations, custom requests
  and audit logs (nullifies circular FKs first to avoid constraint errors)
- Updated create_admin.py to import all models to fix SQLAlchemy registry
